{
  "texts": [
    "The Sentinel Copernicus Browser ( 24) is another popular platform that offers high-225 resolution imagery from the European Space Agency's Sentinel mission, providing global coverage that complements other sources.",
    "Sentinel Hub is a cloud-based platform that stands out for its ease of access to Sentinel imagery and other providers' data, along with robust analysis capabilities via an API (25).",
    "For advanced users, Google Earth Engine (GEE) (26) is a powerful platform that uses JavaScript for accessing and analyzing satellite imagery.",
    "This allows for seamless integration of satellite data into custom scripts for automation and sophisticated geospatial 230 analysis.",
    "GEE is a cloud-based service that provides extensive capabilities for remote sensing data analysis."
  ]
}